fields.content: What a great hackathon! It was a wonderful experience and I would definitely do it again.
My team was brilliant! We had some challenges with getting git working as a team, but pulled together in the end.
Hackathons are a great experience. This was my first hackathon that I have participated in and I would do it all again. A great event, a great idea, a great project.
I liked the hackathon experience, but it was really tough. So much work and I did not really understand how version control works in a team. In the end we got a project out and I am happy about it.

A wonderful experience! Working with other people on a software project is so rewarding. It was really engaging and I am taking so much away from this from version control to deployment. Definitely will do it again!

The communication in my team was not great, there were a lot of inexperienced people and I am not happy with our end product. I do like the concept of a hackathon though. Maybe next time I will be paired with people with more experience.
